LinePlot

hou

2018/9/22

折线图的画法跟散点图差不多，这是在散点图的基础上增加线段。在plot函数中增加一个参数，而在ggplot中则是增加一个图层。

plot

在plot()函数中增加type = 'o'即可画出折线图。 type参数的取值和所画图形： * “p” for points, * “l” for lines, * “b” for both, * “c” for the lines part alone of “b”, * “o” for both ‘overplotted’, * “h” for ‘histogram’ like (or ‘high-density’) vertical lines, * “s” for stair steps, * “S” for other steps, see ‘Details’ below, * “n” for no plotting.

x<-c(2,4,5,7,9,23,33)

y<-c(3,5,6,7,12,14,19)

plot(x,y, type = 'o')

plot(x,y, type = 'h')

plot(x,y, type = 's')

1.1 调整线的类型、粗细、颜色

lty: 类型 lwd: 粗细 col: 颜色

x<-c(2,4,5,7,9,23,33)

y<-c(3,5,6,7,12,14,19)

plot(x,y, type = 'o', lty = 2, lwd =2, col = 'red')

### 增加线段

在原图上增加一条线段，需要使用lines()函数

#先用plot画出画布
x<-c(2,4,5,7,9,23,33)
y<-c(3,5,6,7,12,14,19)
plot(x,y, type = 'o', lty = 2, lwd =2, col = 'red')
# 再增加一条线段
x<-c(2,4,5,7,9,23,33)
y<-c(5,5,6,7,5,6,7)
lines(x,y, type='o', pch = 3)

ggplot2

ggplot画折线图的图层函数是geom_line()

library(ggplot2)
## Warning: package 'ggplot2' was built under R version 3.4.4
q <- ggplot(df, aes(x = x, y = y, color = type))
q + geom_line(aes(linetype = type)) + geom_point()

2.1 改变颜色，粗细，类型

颜色：scale_color_manual(values = c('red','blue')) 类型：scale_linetype_manual(values = c(2,1)) 粗细： geom_line(size = 1.3)

library(ggplot2)
q + geom_line(aes(linetype = type),size= 1.5) + geom_point(size = 3) + scale_color_manual(values = c('red','blue')) + scale_linetype_manual(values = c(2,1))
